{
  "number": "17",
  "lines": [
    {
      "text": "Thy will be done in earth, as it is in heaven.",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": true
    },
    {
      "text": "   _Enable us to know,- as in heaven, so on earth,- God is",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "      omnipotent, supreme_.",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "Give us this day our daily bread;",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": true
    },
    {
      "text": "   _Give us grace for to-day; feed the famished affections;_",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "And forgive us our debts, as we forgive our debtors.",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": true
    },
    {
      "text": "   _And Love is reflected in love;_",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "And lead us not into temptation, but deliver us from",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": true
    },
    {
      "text": "     evil;",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "   _And God leadeth us not into temptation, but delivereth",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "     us from sin, disease, and death._",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "For Thine is the kingdom, and the power, and the",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": true
    },
    {
      "text": "     glory, forever.",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "   _For God is infinite, all-power, all Life, Truth, Love, over",
      "flyout_text": null,
      "paragraph_start": false
    },
    {
      "text": "     all, and All._",
      "flyout_text": "Divine oneness",
      "paragraph_start": false
    }
  ]
}